---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { getContent } from '../lib/content';
const content = await getContent();
---
<Base title="Safety & Terms" description="How Denver Social keeps things safe, friendly, and fair for everyone.">
<div class="c-page">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <header class="c-hero">
    <div class="c-tag">Safety & Terms</div>
    <h1 class="c-title" set:html={content.conduct_title}></h1>
    <p class="c-lede">{content.conduct_subtitle}</p>
  </header>

  <!-- TABLE OF CONTENTS -->
  <nav class="c-toc" aria-label="On this page">
    <span class="c-toc-label">On this page</span>
    <ol>
      <li><a href="#welcome">Everyone's welcome</a></li>
      <li><a href="#safety">How we keep it safe</a></li>
      <li><a href="#women">For women</a></li>
      <li><a href="#line">Where's the line</a></li>
      <li><a href="#hosting">Hosting & reporting</a></li>
      <li><a href="#terms">Terms (the basics)</a></li>
    </ol>
  </nav>

  <!-- EVERYONE -->
  <section class="c-section" id="welcome">
    <h2>Everyone's welcome</h2>
    <p>All ages, all backgrounds, all brain types. Quiet, loud, awkward, outgoing — doesn't matter.</p>
    <div class="c-cards">
      <div class="c-card">
        <span class="c-card-emoji">🧠</span>
        <strong>All brains welcome</strong>
        <p>Neurodivergent, autistic, ADHD, social anxiety — you're good here. Be quiet, leave early, skip small talk. There's no "right way" to hang out.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="c-card">
        <span class="c-card-emoji">👋</span>
        <strong>Show up as you are</strong>
        <p>Half the people here describe themselves as awkward. That's kind of the point. Nobody's performing. Nobody's keeping score.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="c-card">
        <span class="c-card-emoji">💜</span>
        <strong>Not a dating app</strong>
        <p>People are here to make friends. If something happens naturally, cool — but don't come here to hit on people. Read the room.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="c-card">
        <span class="c-card-emoji">🚪</span>
        <strong>Leave whenever</strong>
        <p>Hit your limit? Social battery dead? Just go. You don't owe anyone an explanation. No one will be weird about it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SAFETY -->
  <section class="c-section" id="safety">
    <h2>How we keep it safe</h2>
    <p>A few things are built in by default:</p>
    <ul class="c-list">
      <li><span class="c-icn">📍</span><div><strong>Locations hidden</strong> until you RSVP</div></li>
      <li><span class="c-icn">📞</span><div><strong>Host contact</strong> only shared with confirmed attendees</div></li>
      <li><span class="c-icn">👤</span><div><strong>Every event has a named host</strong> — someone's always accountable</div></li>
      <li><span class="c-icn">✋</span><div><strong>Events are moderated</strong> before going live</div></li>
      <li><span class="c-icn">👥</span><div><strong>Small groups</strong> — usually 6 to 12 people max</div></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- WOMEN -->
  <section class="c-section" id="women">
    <h2>For women</h2>
    <p>We know meetups can feel different if you're a woman. Here's what we want you to know:</p>
    <div class="c-callout c-callout-pos">
      <ul class="c-checks">
        <li><span class="c-check">✓</span>If someone makes you uncomfortable, tell the host or reach out to us. You don't need proof — your word is enough.</li>
        <li><span class="c-check">✓</span>Your info stays private. Other members only see your first name and neighborhood.</li>
        <li><span class="c-check">✓</span>Bring a friend your first time if you want. RSVP for both.</li>
        <li><span class="c-check">✓</span>Most events are in public places. If someone hosts at home, the event says so upfront.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LINE -->
  <section class="c-section" id="line">
    <h2>Where's the line</h2>
    <p>We're pretty relaxed. But if someone says you made them uncomfortable, we're going to listen. These get you removed immediately:</p>
    <div class="c-callout c-callout-neg">
      <ul class="c-checks">
        <li><span class="c-x">✕</span>Harassment or making someone feel unsafe</li>
        <li><span class="c-x">✕</span>Threatening or intimidating anyone</li>
        <li><span class="c-x">✕</span>Following someone after an event</li>
        <li><span class="c-x">✕</span>Sharing someone's location or private info</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="c-aside">Anything else — being rude, too drunk, trying to sell people something — someone will just talk to you about it.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- HOSTING -->
  <section class="c-section" id="hosting">
    <h2>Hosting & reporting</h2>
    <p>Anyone can host. You pick the spot, set the vibe, and help people find you. You're not a bouncer — everyone who shows up is responsible for themselves.</p>
    <p>If something happens at an event, talk to the host, jump in the Discord, or email us. We'll keep it between us.</p>
    <div class="c-btns">
      <a href="https://discord.gg/S8SFNkdSgK" class="c-btn c-btn-discord" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open Discord</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="c-btn c-btn-ghost">Contact us</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TERMS -->
  <section class="c-section" id="terms">
    <h2>Terms (the basics)</h2>
    <p>We're not hiding anything behind legal jargon. Here's how this works:</p>
    <ul class="c-list">
      <li><span class="c-icn">💸</span><div><strong>It's free.</strong> No membership fees, no premium tier, no upsell. Ever.</div></li>
      <li><span class="c-icn">🔒</span><div><strong>Your data.</strong> We store your name and email to run the service. We don't sell it.</div></li>
      <li><span class="c-icn">🍽️</span><div><strong>Event costs.</strong> Some events have costs between you and the venue — Denver Social doesn't take a cut.</div></li>
      <li><span class="c-icn">💰</span><div><strong>Deposits.</strong> Some events require a refundable deposit. Show up → get it back. No-show → forfeited.</div></li>
      <li><span class="c-icn">🚫</span><div><strong>Account removal.</strong> We can remove accounts that violate the rules above.</div></li>
      <li><span class="c-icn">⚠️</span><div><strong>Liability.</strong> Denver Social organizes events but isn't liable for what happens at them. Attend at your own risk.</div></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="c-updated">Last updated: March 2026</p>
  </section>

  <!-- CLOSER -->
  <section class="c-closer">
    <p><strong>Real talk:</strong> Being awkward? Normal. Saying something dumb? Happens. Running late because I-25 is a parking lot? Every single time. This page isn't about being perfect — it's so everyone can relax and have fun.</p>
    <p>If you read this far, you're exactly the kind of person we want around.</p>
    <a href="/events" class="c-btn c-btn-primary">See what's coming up →</a>
  </section>

</div>

<style is:inline>
  .c-page { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px clamp(20px, 4vw, 40px) 96px; }

  /* HERO */
  .c-hero { padding: 16px 0 40px; }
  .c-tag {
    display: inline-block; font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-dim);
    padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .c-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 48px); font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .c-title em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); }
  .c-lede { font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-sec); line-height: 1.55; max-width: 580px; }

  /* TOC */
  .c-toc {
    margin-bottom: 48px; padding: 18px 22px;
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px;
  }
  .c-toc-label {
    display: block; font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-sec); margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .c-toc ol { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 6px 24px; counter-reset: toc; }
  .c-toc li { counter-increment: toc; font-size: 14px; }
  .c-toc li::before { content: counter(toc) ". "; color: var(--text-faint); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .c-toc a { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
  .c-toc a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  @media (max-width: 560px) { .c-toc ol { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  /* SECTIONS */
  .c-section { margin-bottom: 56px; scroll-margin-top: 96px; }
  .c-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .c-section p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text-sec); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .c-section p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .c-section strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; }
  .c-aside { font-size: 14px !important; color: var(--text-faint) !important; margin-top: 14px !important; }

  /* CARD GRID */
  .c-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-top: 16px; }
  .c-card {
    padding: 20px; border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  }
  .c-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .c-card-emoji { font-size: 24px; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .c-card strong { display: block; font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .c-card p { font-size: 14px !important; color: var(--text-sec); line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 0 !important; }
  @media (max-width: 560px) { .c-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  /* LIST WITH ICONS */
  .c-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 16px 0 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .c-list li {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 18px; background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px;
  }
  .c-list li div { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--text-sec); flex: 1; }
  .c-icn { font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.4; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* CALLOUTS */
  .c-callout { padding: 22px 24px; border-radius: 16px; margin-top: 16px; }
  .c-callout-pos { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F5F3FF, #ECFDF5); border: 1px solid #DDD6FE; }
  .c-callout-neg { background: #FEF2F2; border: 1px solid #FECACA; }
  .c-checks { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .c-checks li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--text); }
  .c-check, .c-x {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .c-check { background: #DCFCE7; color: #166534; }
  .c-x { background: #FEE2E2; color: #991B1B; }

  /* BUTTONS */
  .c-btns { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 18px; }
  .c-btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 999px;
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none; transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s, background 0.15s;
  }
  .c-btn-primary { background: var(--cta-bg); color: var(--cta-text); margin-top: 16px; }
  .c-btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 6px 18px var(--accent-glow); }
  .c-btn-discord { background: #5865F2; color: #fff; }
  .c-btn-discord:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(88,101,242,0.32); }
  .c-btn-ghost { background: var(--surface); color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .c-btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--surface-hover); }

  /* CLOSER */
  .c-closer {
    padding: 32px clamp(20px, 4vw, 36px); border-radius: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F0F9FF, #ECFDF5);
    border: 1px solid #BAE6FD;
  }
  .c-closer p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .c-closer p:last-of-type { color: var(--text-sec); }
  .c-closer strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; }

  .c-updated { font-size: 13px !important; color: var(--text-faint) !important; margin-top: 18px !important; }
</style>
</Base>
